        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17475' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Shǐjì', 'Records of the Historian')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">史记</a>
        Records of the Historian (sometimes translated as Records of the Grand Historian) was written by 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17476' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Sīmǎ Qiān', 'Sima Qian')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">司马迁</a> 
