        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17630' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Běn Jì', 'Imperial Biographies')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">本纪</a>
        Imperial Biographies, 10 volumes of <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4172' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎo', 'a table / a form')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>表</a>
        Tables containing timelines of events, 8 volumes of
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=13257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shū', 'document')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>书</a>
        Treatises, 30 volumes of <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17631' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Shì Jiā', 'Biographies of the Feudal Houses and Eminent Persons')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">世家</a>
        Biographies of the Feudal Houses and Eminent Persons, and 70 volumes of
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17478' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lièzhuàn', 'a historical biography')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">列傳</a>
        Biographies and Collective Biographies.
      </p>
