        Biographies of Court Wits.
        Chunyu Kun was an advisor to <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17712' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Qíwēi Wáng', 'King Wei of Qi')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>齐威王</a>
        King Wei of Qi (378 BCE&mdash;320 BCE) during the Warring States Period.
      </p>
