      <p>
        A <a href='/word_detail.php?id=17758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìng', 'a leader of a region of 10 000 people or more')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>令</a>
        Ling commands a region of 10 000 people or more and a <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1322' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǎng', 'director / chief / head / elder')" onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>长</a>
